Interface ProcedureInstance

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, CodeInstance, Copy<TypeObject>, MemberInstance, java.io.Serializable, TypeObject
All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
AnnotationTypeElemInstance_c, ConstructorInstance_c, CovarRetOutputExtensionInfo.CovarRetMethodInstance_c, JL5ConstructorInstance_c, JL5MethodInstance_c, MethodInstance_c, ProcedureInstance_c
public interface ProcedureInstance
extends CodeInstance, MemberInstance
A ProcedureInstance contains the type information for a Java procedure (either a method or a constructor).
